description.en: Haze Finance is BSC’s first DeFi tokens private transaction protocol with yield capability. HAZE token is the native token to Haze Finance, the total supply of HAZE is 1 million. When staking HAZE tokens on our platform, users can earn a share of the protocol fees earned by Haze Finance. HAZE token is also a governance token that allow the holders to vote on the decisions and directions of the protocol.
